WEBVTT

00:00:02.750 --> 00:00:05.350
And she dominates, as if to clear 
away any doubt about her condition!

00:00:05.350 --> 00:00:06.550
Damn it!

00:00:06.550 --> 00:00:09.130
There were concerns about Mejiro 
McQueen's preparation before the race,

00:00:09.130 --> 00:00:12.130
but she had a flawless run, 
setting a record time of 2:03.03!

00:00:12.370 --> 00:00:15.120
McQueen just ran a
picture-perfect return race.

00:00:15.730 --> 00:00:18.260
I wish I could start running again soon.

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:22.340
It really was a perfect run, without the 
slightest sign of trouble, wasn't it?

00:00:22.340 --> 00:00:25.700
I'd certainly agree. It'll be hard not to 
get excited for a possible unprecedented

00:00:25.700 --> 00:00:27.150
third win at the Spring Tennoushou.

00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:28.880
Why Rice Shower, though?

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.470
She just had to ruin it.

00:00:30.470 --> 00:00:33.280
I wanted to see Bourbon win the Triple Crown.

00:00:34.350 --> 00:00:35.400
What a disappointment.

00:00:36.410 --> 00:00:37.740
The champion has returned!

00:00:37.740 --> 00:00:41.180
And her approach to the Spring 
Tennoushou is all clear!

