Bourbon?

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:53.530
Teio-san?

00:12:56.020 --> 00:12:59.570
Your recovery seems to be 
going smoothly, Teio-san.

00:12:59.570 --> 00:13:02.110
Yep. I can even run okay, now.

00:13:02.110 --> 00:13:03.100
How about you?

00:13:03.650 --> 00:13:06.110
Not for the time being.

00:13:06.110 --> 00:13:07.420
I see...

00:13:08.060 --> 00:13:11.140
You got hurt after the Kikkashou, right?

00:13:11.140 --> 00:13:15.250
Yes, when I was training for the Japan Cup.

00:13:15.820 --> 00:13:16.830
I see.

00:13:19.090 --> 00:13:21.860
Rice Shower passes her! 
Rice Shower passes Bourbon!

00:13:21.860 --> 00:13:24.550
There's barely a single length gap 
between them! Rice Shower has the lead!

